title: White House Reporter 'Suspected' to Have Coronavirus
description: A White House reporter who was at the White House multiple times in recent weeks suspected to have coronavirus.
content:
The White House Correspondents Association said in an email that a White House reporter who was at the White House multiple times in recent weeks is suspected to have coronavirus, according to a report on Monday.
